### Summary Table

| Aspect | Details |
|--------|---------|
| **Trigger** | Repost button on post card (hidden if own post) |
| **Auth Required** | Yes (openAuthModal fallback) |
| **Modal Component** | RepostModal.jsx |
| **Optional Caption** | 280 char max |
| **Props Passed to Modal** | journal obj with id, title, users{name, image_url, badge} |
| **Mutation Used** | useRepostMutation |
| **API Endpoint** | POST /api/repost |
